        {
          messageId: '<32353345.1075844447688.JavaMail.evans@thyme>',
          date: 'Wed, 28 Jul 1999 06:20:00 -0700 (PDT)',
          from: 'no.address@enron.com',
          to: '',
          cc: '',
          bcc: '',
          subject: 'Re: Empresa Distribuidora de Energia Norte',
          xFrom: 'Brent Hendry AT ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@CCMAIL',
          xTo: 'Sara Shackleton@ECT, Patricia Cini@ECT',
          xCc: '',
          xBcc: '',
          xFolder: '\\Sara_Shackleton_Dec2000_June2001_1\\Notes Folders\\Argentina',
          xOrigin: 'SHACKLETON-S',
          xFileName: 'sshackle.nsf',
          body: 'Just curious, did this ever go anywhere?\n---------------------- Forwarded by Brent Hendry/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT on\n28/07/99 09:21 AM ---------------------------\n\nFrom: Patricia Cini@ECT on 11/06/99 02:51 PM CDT\n\nTo:   Federico Cerisoli/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\ncc:   Rodolfo Freyre/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Don \nBlack/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Brent \nHendry/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, William S\nBradford/HOU/ECT@ECT\nSubject:  Re: Empresa Distribuidora de Energia Norte  (Document link: Brent\nHendry)\n\nFede-\n\nI am reviewing this counterparty\'s financial statements and will advise.  We \nalso need to run a credit reserve for this transaction you have outlined \nbelow.\n\nRegards,\n\nPat\n\n\n\n\nTo:   Sara Shackleton@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\ncc:   Patricia Cini/HOU/ECT@ECT, Rodolfo \nFreyre/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Don \nBlack/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Brent \nHendry/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Marie\nHeard@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\nSubject:  Re: Empresa Distribuidora de Energia Norte  (Document link: \nPatricia Cini)\n\nSara,\nWe are working with the customer on the subject on the transaction outlined \nbelow.   We need your help putting together the MSA.  Pat will surely contact \nyou with the credit information.  Thank you very much.  Federico.\n\n\n\n\n\nRodolfo Freyre   05/31/99 04:55 PM\n(Embedded image moved to file: pic11719.pcx)\n\nTo:   Patricia Cini/HOU/ECT@ECT\ncc:   Federico Cerisoli/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Don\nBlack/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\n\nSubject:  Re: Empresa Distribuidora de Energi Norte  (Document link: Federico\nCerisoli)\n\n\nPat,\n\nEDEN is a power LDC, owned mainly by AES. We have basically offered them a\nfinancial product that works as described below:\nAttached is a one page description of the structure.\n\n(See attached file: Structure.ppt)\n\nTerms and Conditions of the agreement:\nVolume: 20MW x 7 days a week x 24 hours a day\nTerm: 3 years, 1999\nStart Date: August 1st.\nIndex: Simple hourly average Monomic at Ezeiza\nStructure: "Collar" (Enron sells and EDEN buys):\n- Cap: @$20.15/MWh\n- 1st year, floor: @$18.14/MWh\n- 2nd year, floor: @18.05/MWh\n- 3rd year, floor: @17.96/MWh\nZero-cost call option (Cap) for Enron:  @$22.16/Mwh.  (Enron buys and EDEN \nsells).\n\nExample:\nWhen Index is between $22.16 and $20.15, Enron pays to Eden. If Index is \nabove $22.16, Enron keeps on paying $2.01 (Difference between $22.16 and \n$20.15).\nWhen Index is between $20.15 and the floor (different every year), no \npayments are involved.\nWhen Index is below the floor price, Eden pays to Enron whatever Index minus \nFloor is.\n\nPending issues:\nCredit approval\nMaster Swap Agreement in place\nFinalise negotiations. There is a high probability of this deal happening. \nTiming for closing is close to 10 days.\n\nIf you have any questions, let  me know.\n\nRolo\n\n\n\n\n\nTo:   Rodolfo Freyre/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\ncc:\n\nSubject:  Empresa Distribuidora de Energi Norte\n\nRodolfo-\n\nI received your fax of the financial statements.\n\nWill you please advise on the details of this deal.\n\nThank you,\n\nPat Cini\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n - pic11719.pcx - Structure.ppt',
          path: 'mock\\maildir\\folder-4\\argentina\\17_',
          mainFolder: '',
        },
