          body: 'FYI, see the new legislation section for a summary of the transfer pricing \nresolution.\n---------------------- Forwarded by Brent Hendry/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT on \n02/11/99 08:50 AM ---------------------------\n\n\nbulletin.MNA@mna.com.ar on 01/11/99 08:56:49 PM\nTo: Brent Hendry/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\ncc:  \nSubject: MNA "Energy & Mining Bulletin"  Issue 22\n\n\n - Issue 22.doc',
