- Office Staff\r\ncc: =20\r\nSubject: Michael Guerriero\r\n\r\nTemos o prazer de comunicar que Mike Guerriero aceitou ser realocado em =20\r\nBuenos Aires para chefiar os neg?cios do mercado de commodities, com o t?tu=\r\nlo=20\r\nde Presidente da Enron Argentina.\r\n\r\nMike vem agregar muitos anos de experincia aos nossos neg?cios na ?Argentin=\r\na.  Antes de juntar-se . Enron, Mike trabalhou desde 1986 ?desenvolvendo me=\r\nrcados e companhias de trading nos mercados de privatiza??o ?de energia nos=\r\n Estados Unidos.??Grandes progressos foram atingidos nos neg?cios argentino=\r\ns com grande n?mero ?de clientes e  volumes de transa??es crescendo signifi=\r\ncativamente nos ?ltimos ?dois anos.  Estamos confiantes de que Mike est? in=\r\nstrumentado para levar os ?neg?cios adiante e ajudar a Enron a dominar o me=\r\nrcado de gas e energia na ?Argentina.??Juntem-se a n?s para parabenizar Mik=\r\ne na sua nova posi??o.???Don Black & Scott Porter ?????We are pleased to an=\r\nnounce that Mike Guerriero has agreed to relocate to ?Buenos Aires to head =\r\nthe commodity marketing business for Enron, and assume ?the title of Presid=\r\nent - Enron Argentina.  ??Mike brings many years of energy experience to ou=\r\nr business in Argentina.  ?Prior to joining Enron, since 1986 Mike has been=\r\n growing and building ?marketing and trading companies in the deregulating =\r\nenergy markets of the ?United States.   ??Great progress has been achieved =\r\nin the Argentine business with our number of ?customers and traded volumes =\r\ngrowing significantly in the past 2 years.  We ?are confident that Mike wil=\r\nl be instrumental in taking this business to the ?next level and helping En=\r\nron become the dominant gas and power marketer in ?Argentina.  ??Please joi=\r\nn us in congratulating Mike on his new position.???Don Black & Scott Porter=\r\n????",
