          body: 'Mike who is the country manager would like to you send future updates to the \ndistribution group labeled "Argentina Commercial Staff".  You would also have \nto copy Sami Arap and Don Black since they are in Sao Paulo.  Thanks for your \nhelp on this.\nBrent\n---------------------- Forwarded by Brent Hendry/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT on \n02/03/2000 09:34 AM ---------------------------\n   \n\tEnron International\n\t\n\tFrom:  Michael Guerriero                           02/03/2000 10:24 AM\n\t\n\nTo: Brent Hendry/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\ncc:  \nSubject: Southern Cone Financial Master Agreements Schedule\n\nIf we are going to go with this distribution program let them know to use \nthe  Argentina Commercial Staff  e-mail group address that will automatically \nupdated the people from my team that should be getting the information.\n\nThanks\n\nMFG \n---------------------- Forwarded by Michael Guerriero/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT on \n03/02/2000 07:21 AM ---------------------------\n\n\nRodolfo Freyre\n03/01/2000 05:31 PM\nTo: Michael Guerriero/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\ncc:  \n\nSubject: Southern Cone Financial Master Agreements Schedule\n\n\nFYI.\n---------------------- Forwarded by Rodolfo Freyre/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT on \n03/01/2000 05:31 PM ---------------------------\n\n\nSusan Bailey@ECT\n02/29/2000 05:05 PM\nTo: Sami Arap/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Pablo \nAcevedo/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Bernardo \nAndrews/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Gabriela \nAguilar/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Federico \nCerisoli/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Rodolfo \nFreyre/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Julian \nPoole/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, John J \nShoobridge/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT, Don \nBlack/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT\ncc:  \n\nSubject: Southern Cone Financial Master Agreements Schedule\n\nAll,\n\nSara Shackleton has asked that you all be included on our monthly \ndistribution of the captioned Schedule.  This Schedule is distributed via \ne:mail on the first of every month and sets forth the status of financial \nmaster agreements in Argentina and Brazil.',
